---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cardiovascular Prevention — Dr Delhasse" description="Obesity, cholesterol, diabetes, smoking: the 4 major cardiovascular risk factors and how to manage them." lang="en">

  <section class="hero-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1><span class="text-primary">Prevention</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">The best treatment is the one you avoid</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container detail-content">
      <img src="/images/svg/expertise/prevention.svg" alt="Prevention" class="detail-icon" />

      <p>Four major cardiovascular risk factors:</p>

      <h2>1. Overweight and Obesity</h2>
      <p>Overweight and obesity affect more than 30% of people in industrialised countries. Obesity involves a genetic predisposition and requires a balanced diet combined with regular physical activity to manage risks.</p>

      <h2>2. Blood Lipids / Cholesterol</h2>
      <p>Elevated LDL cholesterol promotes cardiovascular disease, particularly heart attacks and strokes. Diagnosis requires blood tests, and medication is often necessary beyond dietary changes alone.</p>

      <h2>3. Diabetes</h2>
      <p>Type 1 and type 2 diabetes raise blood sugar levels, damaging organ blood vessels. Weight loss helps in type 2, but medications and insulin may be necessary. Blood sugar control reduces the risk of kidney failure, stroke and heart attack.</p>

      <h2>4. Smoking</h2>
      <p>A major risk factor for heart attacks, strokes and cancers. Nicotine substitutes and medications can aid cessation.</p>

      <div class="detail-cta">
        <a href="/en/areas-of-expertise" class="btn btn--outline">&larr; All areas</a>
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book an appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-page { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, #1a3d6d 100%); padding: 6rem 0 4rem; color: var(--color-white); }
  .hero-page h1 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: 2.75rem; }
  .hero-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .detail-content { max-width: 800px; }
  .detail-icon { width: 80px; height: 80px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .detail-content p { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-gray); }
  .detail-content h2 { margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .detail-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-page h1 { font-size: 2rem; } }
</style>
